174
00:11:16,940 --> 00:11:21,940
to thank God that you have done this for us.

175
00:11:21,940 --> 00:11:22,940
Thankfulness.

176
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:27,340
And the thankfulness is the way to joy, there
