spare, but thank Him all the time.

186
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,330
It’s only thankfulness.

187
00:12:07,330 --> 00:12:12,140
And when you thank Him, the waves of joy will
rise within you.

188
00:12:12,140 --> 00:12:15,470
