that,” then you can never enjoy whatever

211
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,020
you have.

212
00:13:45,020 --> 00:13:50,860
And that is what is the message for Christmas
for everyone: is that Christmas is a day of

213
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:57,720
thankfulness because He gave His only son
